<figureCitation box="[518,598,1377,1398]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="12.[303,337,869,888]" captionTargetBox="[280,1105,226,847]" captionTargetId="figure-12@12.[242,1154,168,899]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="Fig. 19. Geographical distribution of the Heterolinus species. Circles = H. basiniger; triangles = H. puncticeps; squares = H. xanthogaster (question mark indicates locality not identified on map)." pageId="6" pageNumber="322">Fig. 19</figureCitation>
)
